== Events == * {{ill|Shōkyō|ja|正暦|12=draft}} 2nd year / {{ill|Genkō|ja|元弘|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft}} [[1333]] {{ill|June 20|ja|6月20日|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Nitta Yoshisada|ja|新田義貞|12=draft}} launched an attack in Ueno Province against the 【Hojo clan|北条氏】, marking the beginning of his campaign (citation needed). * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|12=draft|12=draft}} 15th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft}} [[1587]] {{ill|June 13|ja|6月13日|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Shimazu Yoshihisa|ja|島津義久|12=draft}} surrendered, leading to Toyotomi Hideyoshi’s conquest of Kyushu. * {{ill|Genna|ja|元和|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft}} [[1615]] {{ill|June 4|ja|6月4日|12=draft}}) – During the Osaka Summer Campaign, Toyotomi Hideyori and his consort Yododen committed ritual suicide, marking the end of the Osaka Campaign and the extinction of the Toyotomi clan.
== Births == * ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft}} [[862]] {{ill|June 8|ja|6月8日|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Emperor Xizong|ja|僖宗|12=draft}}, the 18th Emperor of the Tang Dynasty (died [[888]]). * {{ill|Genbun|ja|元文|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft}} [[1737]] {{ill|June 6|ja|6月6日|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Katō Taikan|ja|加藤泰宦|12=draft}}, the 5th lord of the 【Shintani Domain|新谷藩】 (died [[1771]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Shōwa|ja|承和|12=draft}} 7th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft}} [[840]] {{ill|June 11|ja|6月11日|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Junwa Tennō|ja|淳和天皇|12=draft}}, the 53rd Emperor of Japan (born [[786]]). * {{ill|Chōtoku|ja|長徳|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft}} [[995]] {{ill|June 8|ja|6月8日|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Fujiwara Michikane|ja|藤原道兼|12=draft}}, a regent ({{ill|Kanpaku|ja|関白|12=draft|12=draft}}) (born [[961]]). * {{ill|Genna|ja|元和|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft}} 1615, June 4) – Toyotomi Hideyori, son of Toyotomi Hideyoshi (born [[1593]]). * {{ill|Genna|ja|元和|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft}} 1615, June 4) – Yododen, consort of Toyotomi Hideyoshi and mother of Toyotomi Hideyori (born [[1567]]). * ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft}} [[1662]] {{ill|June 23|ja|6月23日|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Zheng Chenggong|ja|鄭成功|12=draft}} (also known as Koxinga), a key figure in the Ming loyalist movement (born [[1624]]). * {{ill|Enpō|ja|延宝|12=draft|12=draft}} 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft}} [[1680]] {{ill|June 4|ja|6月4日|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Ietsuna|ja|徳川家綱|12=draft}}, the 4th shōgun of the Tokugawa shogunate (born [[1641]]).
