[[de:May 8 (Lunisolar)]] [[sn:May 8 (Lunisolar)]] [[ko:음력 5월 8일]] [[ja:5月8日 (旧暦)]] [[zh:五月初八]] [[en:draft:May 8 (Lunisolar)]] [[sn:May 8日 (旧暦)]] [[sn:ay 8 (Lunisolar)]] [[ar:May 8 (Lunisolar)]]
{{citation needed|May 8 (Lunisolar)}}

{{Lunisolar May}} '''May 8''' is the 8th day of the month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)}}, the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜}} day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Shōkyō|ja|正暦}} 2nd year / {{ill|Genkō|ja|元弘}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} [[1333]] {{ill|June 20|ja|6月20日}}) – {{ill|Nitta Yoshisada|ja|新田義貞}} launched an attack in Ueno Province against the 【Hojo clan|北条氏】, marking the beginning of his campaign (citation needed). * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era}} 15th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1587]] {{ill|June 13|ja|6月13日}}) – {{ill|Shimazu Yoshihisa|ja|島津義久}} surrendered, leading to Toyotomi Hideyoshi’s conquest of Kyushu. * {{ill|Genna|ja|元和}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1615]] {{ill|June 4|ja|6月4日}}) – During the Osaka Summer Campaign, Toyotomi Hideyori and his consort Yododen committed ritual suicide, marking the end of the Osaka Campaign and the extinction of the Toyotomi clan.
== Births == * ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} [[862]] {{ill|June 8|ja|6月8日}}) – {{ill|Emperor Xizong|ja|僖宗}}, the 18th Emperor of the Tang Dynasty (died [[888]]). * {{ill|Genbun|ja|元文|1=Genbun}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1737]] {{ill|June 6|ja|6月6日}}) – {{ill|Katō Taikan|ja|加藤泰宦}}, the 5th lord of the 【Shintani Domain|新谷藩】 (died [[1771]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Shōwa|ja|承和}} 7th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} [[840]] {{ill|June 11|ja|6月11日}}) – {{ill|Junwa Tennō|ja|淳和天皇}}, the 53rd Emperor of Japan (born [[786]]). * {{ill|Chōtoku|ja|長徳}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} [[995]] {{ill|June 8|ja|6月8日}}) – {{ill|Fujiwara Michikane|ja|藤原道兼}}, a regent ({{ill|Kanpaku|ja|関白}}) (born [[961]]). * {{ill|Genna|ja|元和}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} 1615, June 4) – Toyotomi Hideyori, son of Toyotomi Hideyoshi (born [[1593]]). * {{ill|Genna|ja|元和}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} 1615, June 4) – Yododen, consort of Toyotomi Hideyoshi and mother of Toyotomi Hideyori (born [[1567]]). * ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1662]] {{ill|June 23|ja|6月23日}}) – {{ill|Zheng Chenggong|ja|鄭成功}} (also known as Koxinga), a key figure in the Ming loyalist movement (born [[1624]]). * {{ill|Enpō|ja|延宝}} 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1680]] {{ill|June 4|ja|6月4日}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Ietsuna|ja|徳川家綱}}, the 4th shōgun of the Tokugawa shogunate (born [[1641]]).
