== Deaths == * {{ill|Shōwa|ja|承和|qq=|qq=draft}} 7th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} [[840]] {{ill|June 11|ja|6月11日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Junwa Tennō|ja|淳和天皇|qq=|qq=draft}}, the 53rd Emperor of Japan (born [[786]]). * {{ill|Chōtoku|ja|長徳|qq=|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} [[995]] {{ill|June 8|ja|6月8日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Fujiwara Michikane|ja|藤原道兼|qq=|qq=draft}}, a regent ({{ill|Kanpaku|ja|関白|qq=|qq=draft}}) (born [[961]]). * {{ill|Genna|ja|元和|qq=|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} 1615, June 4) – Toyotomi Hideyori, son of Toyotomi Hideyoshi (born [[1593]]). * {{ill|Genna|ja|元和|qq=|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} 1615, June 4) – Yododen, consort of Toyotomi Hideyoshi and mother of Toyotomi Hideyori (born [[1567]]). * ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1662]] {{ill|June 23|ja|6月23日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Zheng Chenggong|ja|鄭成功|qq=|qq=draft}} (also known as Koxinga), a key figure in the Ming loyalist movement (born [[1624]]). * {{ill|Enpō|ja|延宝|qq=|qq=draft}} 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1680]] {{ill|June 4|ja|6月4日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Ietsuna|ja|徳川家綱|qq=|qq=draft}}, the 4th shōgun of the Tokugawa shogunate (born [[1641]]).
