|ja|6月4日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 4|qq=}}) – During the Osaka Summer Campaign, Toyotomi Hideyori and his consort Yododen committed ritual suicide, marking the end of the Osaka Campaign and the extinction of the Toyotomi clan.
