ar ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} 1615, June 4) – Yododen, consort of Toyotomi Hideyoshi and mother of Toyotomi Hideyori (born [[1567]]). * ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1662]] {{ill|June 23|ja|6月23日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 23|qq=}}) – {{ill|Zheng Chenggong|ja|鄭成功|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Zheng Chenggong|qq=}} (also known as Koxinga), a key figure in the Ming loyalist movement (born [[1624]]). * {{ill|Enpō|ja|延宝|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Enpō|qq=}} 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1680]] {{ill|June 4|ja|6月4日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 4|qq=}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Ietsuna|ja|徳川家綱|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Ietsuna|qq=}}, the 4th shōgun of the Tokugawa shogunate (born [[1641]]).
