{{Not to be confused with|May 8 (Lunisolar)}}<!--hatnote--> {{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=五月初八|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 5월 8일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar May|qq=}} '''May 8''' is the 8th day of the month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May (Lunisolar)|qq=}}, the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shakkō|qq=}}.
== Events == * [[:en:Shōryaku|Shōkyō]] 2nd year / [[:en:Genkō (1331–1334)|Genkō]] 3rd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[1333]] [[:en:June 20|June 20]]) – [[:en:Nitta Yoshisada|Nitta Yoshisada]] launched an attack in Ueno Province against the 【Hojo clan|北条氏】, marking the beginning of his campaign (citation needed). * [[:en:Tenshō (Momoyama period)|Tenshō Era]] 15th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1587]] [[:en:June 13|June 13]]) – [[:en:Shimazu Yoshihisa|Shimazu Yoshihisa]] surrendered, leading to Toyotomi Hideyoshi’s conquest of Kyushu. * [[:en:Yuanhe|Genna]] 1st year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1615]] [[:en:June 4|June 4]]) – During the Osaka Summer Campaign, Toyotomi Hideyori and his consort Yododen committed ritual suicide, marking the end of the Osaka Campaign and the extinction of the Toyotomi clan.
== Births == * ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[862]] [[:en:June 8|June 8]]) – [[:en:Emperor Xizong of Tang|Emperor Xizong]], the 18th Emperor of the Tang Dynasty (died [[888]]). * [[:en:Genbun|Genbun]] 2nd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1737]] [[:en:June 6|June 6]]) – {{ill|Katō Taikan|ja|加藤泰宦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Katō Taikan|qq=}}, the 5th lord of the 【Shintani Domain|新谷藩】 (died [[1771]]).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Jōwa|Shōwa]] 7th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[840]] [[:en:June 11|June 11]]) – [[:en:Emperor Junna|Junwa Tennō]], the 53rd Emperor of Japan (born [[786]]). * [[:en:Chōtoku|Chōtoku]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[995]] [[:en:June 8|June 8]]) – [[:en:Fujiwara no Michikane|Fujiwara Michikane]], a regent ({{ill|Kanpaku|ja|関白|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanpaku|qq=}}) (born [[961]]). * [[:en:Yuanhe|Genna]] 1st year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] 1615, June 4) – Toyotomi Hideyori, son of Toyotomi Hideyoshi (born [[1593]]). * [[:en:Yuanhe|Genna]] 1st year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] 1615, June 4) – Yododen, consort of Toyotomi Hideyoshi and mother of Toyotomi Hideyori (born [[1567]]). * ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1662]] [[:en:June 23|June 23]]) – [[:en:Koxinga|Zheng Chenggong]] (also known as Koxinga), a key figure in the Ming loyalist movement (born [[1624]]). * [[:en:Enpō|Enpō]] 8th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1680]] [[:en:June 4|June 4]]) – [[:en:Tokugawa Ietsuna|Tokugawa Ietsuna]], the 4th shōgun of the Tokugawa shogunate (born [[1641]]).
