== Events == * [[:en:Shōryaku|Shōkyō]] 2nd year / [[:en:Genkō (1331–1334)|Genkō]] 3rd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1333|1333]] [[:en:June 20|June 20]]) – [[:en:Nitta Yoshisada|Nitta Yoshisada]] launched an attack in Ueno Province against the 【Hojo clan|北条氏】, marking the beginning of his campaign (citation needed). * [[:en:Tenshō (Momoyama period)|Tenshō Era]] 15th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1587|1587]] [[:en:June 13|June 13]]) – [[:en:Shimazu Yoshihisa|Shimazu Yoshihisa]] surrendered, leading to Toyotomi Hideyoshi’s conquest of Kyushu. * [[:en:Yuanhe|Genna]] 1st year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1615]] [[:en:June 4|June 4]]) – During the Osaka Summer Campaign, Toyotomi Hideyori and his consort Yododen committed ritual suicide, marking the end of the Osaka Campaign and the extinction of the Toyotomi clan.
== Births == * ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[862]] [[:en:June 8|June 8]]) – [[:en:Emperor Xizong of Tang|Emperor Xizong]], the 18th Emperor of the Tang Dynasty (died [[888]]). * [[:en:Genbun|Genbun]] 2nd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1737]] [[:en:June 6|June 6]]) – {{ill|Katō Taikan|ja|加藤泰宦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Katō Taikan|qq=}}, the 5th lord of the 【Shintani Domain|新谷藩】 (died [[1771]]).
