{{Not to be confused with|May 8|qq=May 8}}
{{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=五月初八|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 5월 8일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar May|qq=}} '''May 8''' is the 8th day of the month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May (Lunisolar)|qq=}}, the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shakkō|1=Shakkō|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q11635368}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Shōryaku|en|Shōryaku|qid=Q1324858|lt=Shōkyō|1=Shōryaku}} 2nd year / {{ill|Genkō (1331–1334)|en|Genkō (1331–1334)|qid=Q1194556|lt=Genkō|1=Genkō (1331–1334)}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1333|en|1333|qid=Q6004|lt=1333|1=1333}} {{ill|June 20|en|June 20|qid=Q2666|lt=June 20|1=June 20}}) – {{ill|Nitta Yoshisada|en|Nitta Yoshisada|qid=Q1328796|lt=Nitta Yoshisada|1=Nitta Yoshisada}} launched an attack in Ueno Province against the 【Hojo clan|北条氏】, marking the beginning of his campaign (citation needed). * {{ill|Tenshō (Momoyama period)|en|Tenshō (Momoyama period)|qid=Q1145058|lt=Tenshō Era|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)}} 15th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1587|en|1587|qid=Q6744|lt=1587|1=1587}} {{ill|June 13|en|June 13|qid=Q2614|lt=June 13|1=June 13}}) – {{ill|Shimazu Yoshihisa|en|Shimazu Yoshihisa|qid=Q955727|lt=Shimazu Yoshihisa|1=Shimazu Yoshihisa}} surrendered, leading to Toyotomi Hideyoshi’s conquest of Kyushu. * {{ill|Yuanhe|en|Yuanhe|qid=Q10889567|lt=Genna|1=Yuanhe}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1615|en|1615|qid=Q6784|lt=1615|1=1615}} {{ill|June 4|en|June 4|qid=Q2627|lt=June 4|1=June 4}}) – During the Osaka Summer Campaign, Toyotomi Hideyori and his consort Yododen committed ritual suicide, marking the end of the Osaka Campaign and the extinction of the Toyotomi clan.
== Births == * ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|862|en|862|qid=Q24993|lt=862|1=862}} {{ill|June 8|en|June 8|qid=Q2621|lt=June 8|1=June 8}}) – {{ill|Emperor Xizong of Tang|en|Emperor Xizong of Tang|qid=Q9889|lt=Emperor Xizong|1=Emperor Xizong of Tang}}, the 18th Emperor of the Tang Dynasty (died {{ill|888|en|888|qid=Q563006|lt=888|1=888}}). * {{ill|Genbun|en|Genbun|qid=Q1145754|lt=Genbun|1=Genbun}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1737|en|1737|qid=Q6993|lt=1737|1=1737}} {{ill|June 6|en|June 6|qid=Q2620|lt=June 6|1=June 6}}) – {{ill|Katō Taikan|ja|加藤泰宦|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Katō Taikan|1=Katō Yasunobu|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q11399357}}, the 5th lord of the 【Shintani Domain|新谷藩】 (died {{ill|1771|en|1771|qid=Q7686|lt=1771|1=1771}}).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Jōwa|en|Jōwa|qid=Q3577279|lt=Shōwa|1=Jōwa}} 7th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|840|en|840|qid=Q29936|lt=840|1=840}} {{ill|June 11|en|June 11|qid=Q2617|lt=June 11|1=June 11}}) – {{ill|Emperor Junna|en|Emperor Junna|qid=Q374136|lt=Junwa Tennō|1=Emperor Junna}}, the 53rd Emperor of Japan (born {{ill|786|en|786|qid=Q30307|lt=786|1=786}}). * {{ill|Chōtoku|en|Chōtoku|qid=Q1327213|lt=Chōtoku|1=Chōtoku}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|995|en|995|qid=Q23794|lt=995|1=995}} {{ill|June 8|en|June 8|qid=Q2621|lt=June 8|1=June 8}}) – {{ill|Fujiwara no Michikane|en|Fujiwara no Michikane|qid=Q366253|lt=Fujiwara Michikane|1=Fujiwara no Michikane}}, a regent ({{ill|Kanpaku|ja|関白|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanpaku|1=kampaku|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q1199966}}) (born {{ill|961|en|961|qid=Q23881|lt=961|1=961}}). * {{ill|Yuanhe|en|Yuanhe|qid=Q10889567|lt=Genna|1=Yuanhe}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} 1615, June 4) – Toyotomi Hideyori, son of Toyotomi Hideyoshi (born {{ill|1593|en|1593|qid=Q6772|lt=1593|1=1593}}). * {{ill|Yuanhe|en|Yuanhe|qid=Q10889567|lt=Genna|1=Yuanhe}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} 1615, June 4) – Yododen, consort of Toyotomi Hideyoshi and mother of Toyotomi Hideyori (born {{ill|1567|en|1567|qid=Q6642|lt=1567|1=1567}}). * ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1662|en|1662|qid=Q7574|lt=1662|1=1662}} {{ill|June 23|en|June 23|qid=Q2668|lt=June 23|1=June 23}}) – {{ill|Koxinga|en|Koxinga|qid=Q197615|lt=Zheng Chenggong|1=Koxinga}} (also known as Koxinga), a key figure in the Ming loyalist movement (born {{ill|1624|en|1624|qid=Q6821|lt=1624|1=1624}}). * {{ill|Enpō|en|Enpō|qid=Q1145735|lt=Enpō|1=Enpō}} 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1680|en|1680|qid=Q7642|lt=1680|1=1680}} {{ill|June 4|en|June 4|qid=Q2627|lt=June 4|1=June 4}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Ietsuna|en|Tokugawa Ietsuna|qid=Q323422|lt=Tokugawa Ietsuna|1=Tokugawa Ietsuna}}, the 4th shōgun of the Tokugawa shogunate (born {{ill|1641|en|1641|qid=Q6907|lt=1641|1=1641}}).
